To test hx,

cat filename | hx | less

echo string | hx

Example:

echo "The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog" | hx 

000000  54686520 71756963  6b206272 6f776e20  *The quick brown *
000010  666f7820 6a756d70  73206f76 65722074  *fox jumps over t*
000020  6865206c 617a7920  646f670a           *he lazy dog     *

Example:

cat inst.sh | hx

000000  23212f62 696e2f62  6173680a 6d616b65  *#!/bin/bash make*
000010  202d6620 68782e6d  616b0a             * -f hx.mak      *

